---
import OldWebLayout from '@/layouts/OldWebLayout.astro';
---
<OldWebLayout title="House Rules" section="houserules">

  <p class="hr-eyebrow">Posted 1996. Not updated since. Still in effect.</p>

  <h1>House Rules</h1>

  <p class="hr-lede">
    Some rules are not posted on purpose. The unposted ones still apply.
  </p>

  <ol class="hr-list">
    <li>House rules apply. Even when nobody is enforcing them.</li>
    <li>Call your own fouls. Management is not watching. The room is.</li>
    <li>No coaching from the rail. Bystanders do not get a vote.</li>
    <li>Scratch on the break: rack stays. Cue ball comes back to the kitchen. So do you.</li>
    <li>Three fouls and you're filed. Not removed. Filed.</li>
    <li>Argue a call and we laugh. Press it and we stop.</li>
    <li>The phone behind the bar is not a customer service line. Do not pick it up unless you mean it.</li>
    <li>Online payment is broken. Insert quarters at the counter. Exact change preferred. Machine does not give change. Machine may not exist.</li>
    <li>The clock reads 1:47. It will read 1:47 at last call. That is not a malfunction.</li>
    <li>Tip the bartender. Tipping will not move you up the list. Not tipping will move you down.</li>
    <li>If a door moves, you did not see a door move.</li>
    <li>Management decisions are final. Management may not be present.</li>
  </ol>

  <p class="hr-stamp">FILED. NOT REMOVED. — Management</p>

  <p class="hr-coda">
    Posted on the back wall, near the cigarette machine.
    Wording has not changed since the lease was signed.
    The lease has not been signed.
  </p>

</OldWebLayout>

<style>
  .hr-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--type-mono, 'JetBrains Mono', monospace);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--ink-fade, #5a513f);
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 56px);
  }

  .hr-lede {
    font-family: var(--type-paper, Georgia, serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    color: var(--ink, #14110e);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--ink, #14110e);
    padding-left: 14px;
  }

  .hr-list {
    font-family: var(--type-paper, Georgia, serif);
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 64ch;
    margin: 0 0 36px;
    padding-left: 28px;
    counter-reset: hr-counter;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .hr-list li {
    counter-increment: hr-counter;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hr-list li::before {
    content: counter(hr-counter, decimal-leading-zero) ". ";
    position: absolute;
    left: -32px;
    width: 28px;
    text-align: right;
    font-family: var(--type-mono, monospace);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-fade, #5a513f);
    top: 4px;
  }

  .hr-stamp {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 4px 0 28px;
    padding: 10px 18px 8px;
    font-family: var(--type-mono, 'JetBrains Mono', monospace);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: #a01818;
    border: 2.5px solid #a01818;
    transform: rotate(-1.8deg);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(160, 24, 24, 0.25);
  }

  .hr-coda {
    font-family: var(--type-mono, monospace);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink-fade, #5a513f);
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--ink-fade, #5a513f);
  }
</style>
